item.title: Sydney
item.description: Sydney This is probably the third time I’ve been in Sydney. I’m only here for a few days but my thoughts on Sydney are usually pretty negative. Lucky this time I have a guide in the form of friends! Vic, Alas, Russ helped me around this massive city. Fishburners A startup space recommended by a friend of mine back in Perth. Its the only space that directly supports startups only, and does not accept small businesses or consultants.
